Comment: 0,0:03:28.98,0:03:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,==============================================MAIN====================================================
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,AR诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.50,0:03:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,启动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.01,0:03:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是战场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:03:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但真不愧是泽田
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,大家没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.68,0:04:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.98,0:04:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.23,0:04:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,看来AR诱饵很有效果啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.53,0:04:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.40,0:04:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,导弹不管用的话就没什么好怕的了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,要靠近吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,别 并不是所有的导弹都没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.34,0:04:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,AR诱饵的作用是干涉居夫让其以为AR是本体
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.43,0:04:23.97,Default,,0,0,0,,从而难以确定目标
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.67,0:04:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,说白了就像是分身术一样的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然中弹的可能性很低
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.05,0:04:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但也会有碰巧击中本体的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.03,0:04:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,来啦!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.50,0:04:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,小秋 按钮！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.06,0:04:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,阿海！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.28,0:05:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,没事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.59,0:05:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,铁枪突刺被…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.37,0:05:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,还有右边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.72,0:05:39.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你要逃跑吗 美沙姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.62,0:05:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,SUMERAGI与大型活动物体交战中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,火箭没有异常
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.62,0:05:44.45,Default,,0,0,0,,倒计时继续
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.36,0:05:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我会看准时机突破进去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.95,0:05:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,请掩护我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.95,0:05:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,还有…30分钟…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.59,0:06:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这个距离的话就不能发射导弹了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样吧 美沙姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.06,0:06:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.38,0:06:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.86,0:06:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心 不可能输的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.79,0:06:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那可是我调整的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.74,0:06:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,咆哮吧 磁单极子马达
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.48,0:06:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.16,0:07:02.70,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.25,0:07:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,还没完
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.16,0:07:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,小秋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,钢巴莱鲁十字拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.20,0:07:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,打中了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.44,0:07:57.32,Default,,0,0,0,,应该是破坏了镜头部分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:07:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,如此一来…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.90,0:08:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,美沙姐 能听见吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.48,0:08:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.97,0:08:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,出来向小秋…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.47,0:08:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,自己对小秋说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.73,0:08:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,到底发生了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.51,0:08:17.37,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要抛弃钢巴制作
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要说那种话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,全部 全部说出来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,小秋就是为了听你说这些才追逐到现在的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.85,0:08:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,而且追上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.93,0:08:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,阿海…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,别逃避啊 美沙姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.40,0:08:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,很遗憾你晚了一步
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.23,0:08:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,她的意识已经彻底崩坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我已经把她打入了黑暗的深渊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.93,0:09:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,自爆？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,快看！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.60,0:09:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,她只是个没有意识的操线人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.19,0:09:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,属于我君岛皇的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.14,0:09:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,君岛皇…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是B组
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.54,0:09:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,成功夺回控制室
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.50,0:09:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,现在开始取消火箭发射
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.29,0:09:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,没用的 火箭是不会停止的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.78,0:09:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,什么…！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,因为实验必须成功
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.41,0:09:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好快！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.83,0:10:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,跳起来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.54,0:10:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,大家快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.24,0:10:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.46,0:10:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是的死了 刚刚死了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.23,0:10:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,大家没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,还好 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.22,0:10:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,很遗憾 之后只能依靠内置电池了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,驱动时间大概5分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.41,0:10:52.26,Default,,0,0,0,,秋穗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.98,0:10:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 不管试多少次都不接受中止发射的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.33,0:10:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,被管理员阻挡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.65,0:11:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的管理员是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.83,0:11:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,君岛皇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.77,0:11:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,这可是倾注了这么多时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.71,0:11:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,连我的命都搭进去的实验
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.84,0:11:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,必须要成功
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.27,0:11:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,必须
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.28,0:11:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,什么东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.42,0:11:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,来 来…来啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.58,0:11:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,泽田 终于来啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.62,0:11:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,神代 现在不是开玩笑的时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.24,0:11:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 程序来啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.84,0:11:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,删除君岛皇的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.12,0:11:42.25,Default,,0,0,0,,要使用该程序
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.92,0:11:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,需安装完毕后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.19,0:11:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,在口袋机上映有君岛皇AR的状态下锁机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,但是在此之前
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,安装后需要重启口袋机
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.13,0:12:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,重启？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.06,0:12:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.07,0:12:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,然后想办法把姐姐从驾驶舱里拉出来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.54,0:12:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一来君岛皇肯定会映在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.32,0:12:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,可别发现啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,还剩10分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.96,0:12:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,通信完全被阻断了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是动了什么手脚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.21,0:12:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,没反应？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.02,0:13:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:02.21,Default,,0,0,0,,被发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.26,0:13:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,阿海
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.41,0:13:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,部长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:06.39,Default,,0,0,0,,八汐学长正在重启
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,完全看不见对方的动作
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,阿海…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.53,0:13:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,部长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.37,0:13:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐… 姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.15,0:13:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐！住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.92,0:13:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,住手吧 姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.43,0:13:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,是我啊 小秋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.03,0:13:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能 还有意识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.21,0:14:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,小秋 退下！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.33,0:14:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧 美沙姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.77,0:14:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,快打过来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.81,0:14:13.99,Default,,0,0,0,,美沙姐不是电视上向别人示好的类型吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.36,0:14:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是个会板着脸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.93,0:14:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,毫不留情地完胜别人的冷酷的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,阿海…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.28,0:14:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,明明是个女生却爱看机器人动画
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.66,0:14:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,在这种乡下居然还真的要做大型机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.57,0:14:30.41,Default,,0,0,0,,把周围的人都连累进来的混蛋女人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.58,0:14:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,现在的你有什么属于自己的正确资质啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.19,0:14:36.64,Default,,0,0,0,,快回答我啊 美沙姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.34,0:14:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你要是再敢乱说下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.49,0:14:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就把你灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,好 从现在开始就是我们的游戏了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂的 美沙姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.78,0:14:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill Ballad的时候总是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.22,0:15:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,小秋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.67,0:15:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,美沙姐一定会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.07,0:15:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,向右边偏4帧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:15:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.12,0:16:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.04,0:16:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,很遗憾 美沙希已经不在了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.49,0:16:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这次一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.86,0:16:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,快看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.65,0:16:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这是钢巴制作1
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.45,0:16:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,是姐姐一直在做的机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.32,0:16:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是来说这个的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.75,0:16:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这是饱含姐姐和我 还有大家的思念的机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.34,0:16:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,现在动起来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.96,0:16:27.20,Default,,0,0,0,,它要拯救世界呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.35,0:16:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,看来姐妹两个都有着奇妙的思维啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.98,0:16:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,这是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.44,0:16:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸第一次给我看机器人的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.47,0:16:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐是这么说的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.11,0:16:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,在这个世上最喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.10,0:16:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,现在…也喜欢吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:17:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐 现在也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,在这个世上最喜欢机器人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.42,0:17:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,住嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.77,0:17:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,还差…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.56,0:17:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,还差一点点就成了 真遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.39,0:17:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…还有第二 第三个我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.27,0:17:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,总有一天…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.77,0:17:45.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,即便如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.04,0:17:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,正义好像是必胜的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.73,0:17:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的部长是这么说的
